      "text": [
        " ثَقْبُ أُذُنِ الْغُلَامِ مِنَ السُّنَّةِ وَ خِتَانُ الْغُلَامِ مِنَ السُّنَّةِ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "And from him, from Ahmad Bin Muhammad Bin Isa, from Muhammad Bin Isa, from Abdullah Bin Sinan, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘Piercing the ear of the boy is from the Sunnah, and circumcision of the boy is from the Sunnah’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "5. It is narrated from the narrator of the previous Hadith from Ahmad ibn Muhammad ibn ‘Isa from ‘Abd Allah ibn Sinan who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘Piercing the ears of a boy is of the Sunnah as well as his circumcision.’” "
        ]
      }
